Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, let's start with the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Test-sama.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:48.65,0:01:53.65,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2C3042&\3c&HDFE3D2&\b0\pos(265.17,184)}Test
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's good to be home.{/I just returned}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to take a bath? \NOr do you want to eat first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this hot water is so nice...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You can afford being carefree, \Nfree of any tests!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, come take a bath with us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of being made fun of \Nas a 0-point bozo up until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've studied this time around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But the worst has yet to come - \Nwhen my results come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.31,0:02:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Just what you'd expect! 95 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Always getting perfect scores feels trite. \NI do other numbers too for diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have 98!{last part sounds like yon (4), not yo (hey)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Iyona-chan with a perfect score of 100 points, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own score is just as amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone performed so well on this test!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Jabao's score?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao is my only ray of hope. {/star}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how bad my score is, \Nat the very least I won't flunk it as hard as he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! 55 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What score again?!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Jabao scored 55 points?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:15.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H93D4C7&\3c&H8941C0&\pos(659.71,209.6)}Eek! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao, my eternal companion in the "0-point-brotherhood," got 55?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When I put my mind to it, I can do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a great job, Jabao-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It sucks to be always \Nassociated with Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you need to study to grow up - \Never heard of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of Jabao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching the gist of it in a snap of a finger! {no clue what good place he set his eyes on, assumed "you've got a good point"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, we live in an age of academic society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jabao got 55 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm under enormous pressure right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Edojo Honmaru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,0 points...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako got 95.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,100 for Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa is at 98.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Jabao scored 55 on this test...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone sees my 0 points, \Nthey'll be laughing out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, good luck with the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Life isn't all about test scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Through Taru's special trainings and kenpo, \Nhe managed to develop a strong side or two.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually thought he was improving, \Nbut really, his brains were shrinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:05:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy. 0 points again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I even feel bad for\Nmistreating someone as incapacitated as you.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So no amount of magic can help him? \NThis is all he got... {}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They say there's no cure for stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But seeing how perfectly incorrigible he is, \NI'm starting to feel kinda sorry for him.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Iyona-chan is giving me a condescending look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Better just make fun of me and mock me \Nand laugh out loud openly like you always did before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even getting laughed at was still better than this! {better; preferable; less objectionable; least-worst}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, a beautiful bright red sunset in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a freshly baked takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it's the shining "0 points," Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, cheer up. There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been sighing heavily since this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not feeling unwell, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just thinking, \Nmaybe I should go on a diet or something like that...{/try some diet }{no clue how'd that help his test scores} {tlc this and the rest of lines in this scene, not sure if I'm getting this whole diet thing right}{6:39: I'm hearing "いや、ちょとダイエットなんかしてみようかな"\NA loose TL would be something like "Oh, I was just thinking, maybe I should go on a diet"\NHe's just making an excuse here since his Dad's asking him what's wrong.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this effeminate bullshit? {/what are you saying despite being a man}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, it's a given for girls, \Neven in elementary school, to be on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So boys doing that sometimes \Nis nothing special either. {no clue how that proves dieting manly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, dinner is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll also cheer up after you've eaten! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it! Do more, more. {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru in the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rub-rub, cheer up! There! {scrubbing hard; scrubbing clean}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that? Honmaru cheered up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you wake up, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This - WhaTVer are we watching today? Telewhere. {どこでもてれび どーしてるん}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a TV that lets you watch whatever you want \Nany time of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, it's Iyona taking a morning shower. \NWow, it's Iyona herself! {dazo}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru's favorite nude Iyona!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better, Honmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A morning shower, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan sure loves keeping herself clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Even nude Iyona's not helping... \NHonmaru seriously depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's give you some emboldening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How has it been going? {g, would assume some archaic dialect}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru not cheerful. \NPlease give him your emboldening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. You can leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Honmaru-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up at once, Honmaru-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-dono is truly the man this world needs the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you lose your spirits \Nover matters so insignificant?!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, my whole body is filled with strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Life has its hardships and its pleasures!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The secret is not to run away when facing a difficulty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who stands fast and fights back \Nis the one who can call himself a man!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I ever be stopped by something like this?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the man Edojo Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to school and study hard, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got 0 points, so what about that?! \NWhen you're at the bottom, the only way to go is up! {h}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll climb and climb, until I can score 100 or 200, \Nor even 10,000 points, I'll keep climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Honmaru on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Maddemboldening Samurai, \NMuchaha Gemasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hear him yelling at you, \Nyou become madly emboldened and feel better at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Muchaha-sama, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming too! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Isn't it Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Morn', Iyona-chan!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? \NFeeling dispirited, Iyona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend, angelfish Payan-chan, died.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Muchaha-sama, counting on your emboldening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, feel free to leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-dono, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All who live will die someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than mourn the parting, cherish the memories \Nyou made together while they were alive!{/living together}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, etch it in your mind that you must live \Neach moment to the fullest from now on too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! No matter how sad I am, \Nit won't bring Payan-chan back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, I will cherish each moment of my own life, \Nwith memories of them forever in my heart!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Iyona on fire too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll support you by swimming too!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Neyo! You don't look cheerful. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,'Preciate the attention and stuff, but unlike you,\NI can't be carefree for no reason. Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Muchaha-sama, your services are needed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up at once, Zakenja Neyo-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For I have the most recent insight \Ninto the matter distressing you right now!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The one constantly on your mind, Nezo-dono, \Nis doing well and perfectly fine! {/troubling/worrying you}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dwelling in a mountain retreat, \NNezo-dono strives to overcome himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Day and night, he's putting \Nhis every effort into training!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, having acquired even more marvelous kenpo \Nand changed beyond recognition, he'll be back home{ no doubt about it}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Nezo-dono comes home, starved, \Na delicious meal must be waiting for him there!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The duty of preparing it falls on you!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved, Nezo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Neyo also on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting, Nezo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have as much meat and potatoes as you want! {/I'll make your favorite ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I got a whopping 55 points yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but mom still wouldn't give me any pocket money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I thought I'd buy and play \Nthat newly released game{ software}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no other interesting games \Nto play these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep churning out new ones.{tlc, no clue what he means, assumed some reference to a game of the time about toilets or something? though I don't remember that episode of AVGN}{15:39: I'm hearing "新しいといれだな"\NI have no clue. I know I'm hearing "toilet" but that doesn't make any sense considering the context.\NMaybe Jabao's saying his allowance is going to be used to buy a new toilet.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All boring, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of Jabao and Korekiyo's moods as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Jabao-dono, Korekiyo-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.36,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumo, sir! Sumo is more fun than any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And the proof of that \Nis that it's Japan's national sport!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! The most popular sport right now is sumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us all stay forever young and sturdy! To battle! {g, no clue what's this wakataka}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! It's true what they say. \NSumo is the ultimate martial arts for entertainment! {assumed 相撲こそまさに娯楽の横綱 but nc what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With it, you wouldn't even wanna \Nlook at all the other games!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryoguchiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Belt grab!{nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good! Yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's embolden everyone around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, to battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I got 95 points and Iyona-san got 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm a whole 5 points behind, \NI'm not qualified to love Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please embolden Harako too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just bought this uniform! {using new tools (or clothes, etc.); new tools (or clothes, etc.) - no clue what it means}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, no need to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a serious injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a cloudburst is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should stop just in case? {/for the risk of catching a cold}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone at school, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up at once, great many of folk! {no clue, was minna no shuu in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll study hard so that I don't slip up, \Nscoring 95 ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I must score the same 100 points as Iyona-san \Nand not a point less!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who even cares if the clothes are new or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman's strength is in her body \Nwhich is under the clothes!{no clue what she means by shoubu}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shape up, shape up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Looking good, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fortify your body, \Nyou won't ever be afraid of injuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain or no rain, it's all the same to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We ain't so delicate as to catch a cold!{h}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.72,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun! The Warbler cries, \N"Let's move to Heian-kyo" - 794 CE! {no clue like at all, found this https://www.t-konan.net/members/20210415_onomatope_no4/ as seemingly it's not supposed to make much sense even to japanese and who tf knows the history of japan, amrite?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's build a good country" - \NKamakura School District, 1192!{same}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"A good man is he who doesn't even kill insects," \NTaika Reforms of 645 CE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo! Better come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Everyone motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid, splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic wore off after ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! All my hair fell out\Nand my head is as smooth as a melon! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Taru's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! What the hell did you do to us all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right. I remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Maddemboldening Samurai Muchaha Gemasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone emboldened. Everyone emboldened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone boldened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone balded!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Counting on you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.66,0:20:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up you, great many of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you even care any for your head's baldness?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The best we could do is to laugh at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you all, having your heads\Nso smooth and shiny like the temple monks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is true!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels great to go home with a clear and fresh head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty good on you, Jabao!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true for anyone, Harako! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Always so neat and clean!{}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.99,0:20:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super trendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Everyone is okay being bald!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. That's the spirit, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Today at Nannosho Elementary School, \Na peculiar incident occurred, during which,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,all the pupils and teachers, dressed and shaved like monks, \Nwere dancing and laughing out loud in the schoolyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ministry of Education took this situation seriously \Nand an investigation committee was assembled...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Honmaru, they showed us on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some way to fix my haircut, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair will grow back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say, "Yes, yes..." {}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I was such an idiot \Nfor counting on magic to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no way to go. \NCheer up, you!{nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No, I don't need no more emboldening, I assure you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cheerful enough as it is, just look, I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See? See? See? Like this, like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, study! Study!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, I'm not getting 0 points ever again, goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid, splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru studying with enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.32,0:22:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui, where the hell did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know how much \Nyour big brother is worried for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Honmaru! Dead end, not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Rui go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Dead end here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing after all that searching! {}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish siblings wouldn't quarrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:22:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:22:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijigawa's Sibling Duty. {伊知川の兄妹仁義}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Rui, I won't let you feel lonely ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:04.14,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 85 \NIjigawa's Sibling Duty {伊知川の兄妹仁義}
